---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import PageHero from "../../components/PageHero.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms · LUZ Impacto" description="LUZ Impacto Foundation terms of use.">
  <Header />

  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Terms of use."
    lede="The conditions under which this website is used."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="intro-humana">
        Here are the basic rules for using the site and for donating.
        <strong>In plain English:</strong> use the content with respect, donations
        are voluntary, and if anything is unclear,
        <a href="mailto:samuel@luzimpacto.org">message us</a> and we'll clarify.
      </div>

      <p class="updated">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <h2>About LUZ Impacto</h2>
      <p>
        LUZ Impacto Foundation is a Costa Rican evangelical Christian ministry.
        We're not a church — we're a bridge between young people who receive Christ
        in Costa Rica's schools and the local churches that can disciple them.
      </p>

      <h2>Site use</h2>
      <p>
        This website (<strong>luzimpacto.org</strong>) is for free and informational use.
        By using it, you accept:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>That published information is informational and may change over time.</li>
        <li>Not to use the site's content for commercial, political, or misleading purposes.</li>
        <li>Not to impersonate LUZ Impacto Foundation or its team.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Donations</h2>
      <p>
        Donations to LUZ Impacto are <strong>voluntary</strong> and go exclusively
        to the ministry's mission: transportation, materials, equipment, and events
        in Costa Rica's schools.
      </p>
      <p>
        Donations are <strong>non-refundable</strong> except in cases of documented
        technical error. If you have any question or want to reverse a donation made
        in error, message us at
        <a href="mailto:samuel@luzimpacto.org">samuel@luzimpacto.org</a> within 7 days.
      </p>
      <p>
        Donations do not constitute a commercial obligation or purchase of services.
        They are voluntary gifts to the ministry.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        The name <strong>"LUZ Impacto"</strong>, the logo, and original site texts are property
        of LUZ Impacto Foundation. Photographs are from our own events. The map of
        Costa Rica used on the site comes from Wikimedia Commons under CC BY-SA license.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        LUZ Impacto makes reasonable efforts to keep site information accurate and current,
        but does not guarantee it is free of errors. Use of the site is at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any inquiry about these terms, message us at
        <a href="mailto:samuel@luzimpacto.org">samuel@luzimpacto.org</a> or by WhatsApp at
        <a href="https://wa.me/50685493929" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+506 8549 3929</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Jurisdiction</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of Costa Rica.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .narrow { max-width: 760px; }
  .intro-humana {
    background: var(--crema);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--yellow);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .intro-humana strong { color: var(--charcoal); }
  .intro-humana a { color: var(--charcoal); font-weight: 600; }
  .updated {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
  p, li { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  ul { padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  a { color: var(--charcoal); font-weight: 500; }
  strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
